{
  "stem": "20609.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so by-- we were-- I was scheduled to leave on February the 6th, 1940.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Lo and behold, my father gets released on sometime the last week of January.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Out of the-- he was in a place called Sachsenhausen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was released with the understanding that within 30 days, he leaves Germany.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At that time, Jews were still allowed to leave.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And some had places where they could go to.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so my father at that time went to the Jewish center, and he was assigned on the next boat-- those were illegal transports going to Israel to break the blockade.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "At that time, the English still had a blockade.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The Jewish organization had steam-- had riverboats which went-- some of them amusement or freighters and things like that-- went on the Danube, all the way through Hungary or Czechoslovakia, all the way to Romania to the Black Sea.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And supposedly at that time, some big ship was going to pick them up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Well, the winter of '39, '40 was one of the coldest winter almost in the history of Europe.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The Danube was frozen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So my father couldn't-- couldn't leave.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He was supposed to immediately for Vienna to get put in the transport there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And-- and then something amazing happened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "At that time, also like about the end of January, my sister pops up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "What happened was her and her girlfriend met some German soldiers there and told them a story like we were tourists.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We lost all our papers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we are from Berlin.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And you know, all they spoke was German without an accent and everything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they'd like to get back to Germany.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And this guy says, well, my truck is going.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Go ahead.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Jump on the truck.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
